column16: Ryan Zimmerman flies into double play, right fielder Michael Cuddyer to catcher Wilin Rosario to third baseman Jordan Pacheco.    Jesus Flores out at home.
Bryce Harper singles on a ground ball to third baseman Jordan Pacheco.
Danny Espinosa grounds out softly to first baseman Tyler Colvin.    Jesus Flores to 3rd.    Mark DeRosa to 2nd.
Mark DeRosa walks.    Jesus Flores to 2nd.
Jesus Flores singles on a sharp line drive to right fielder Michael Cuddyer.
Nate McLouth flies out to center fielder Dexter Fowler.
Alex Presley grounds out, shortstop Troy Tulowitzki to first baseman Todd Helton.    Rod Barajas to 3rd.
Charlie Morton out on a sacrifice bunt, first baseman Todd Helton to second baseman Marco Scutaro.    Rod Barajas to 2nd.
Rod Barajas singles on a pop up to first baseman Todd Helton.
